title: Wheat straw bundling machine US-9YFQ-3043A

short_description: This US-9YFQ-3043A wheat straw baler is 3050mm long, 740mm wide and 1750mm high. The press is square shaped, and the length of straw presses ranges from 300 mm to 1200 mm.
